title: Top Five Summer 2021 Movies and Everything Sean Missed While He Was Out
description:
Sean returns from his break and Amanda runs down the major story lines from the world of movies that he missed (0:31). Then, they share their favorite (and not so favorite) movies of the summer (48:30).

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Producer: Bobby Wagner
